==================
  Kyoko Hitsugaya
==================
Name: Kyoko Hitsugaya "Koko"
Age: 21 years old
College Degree: Studying Psychology
Hitsugaya Kyoko, born and raised in Tokyo. Currently studying psychology in the most renowed university in the entire Japan, Central University of Tokyo (CUT). Before she finishes the course one of Koko's teacher asked her to help him on a project about autist people, saying that it would be a great addition to her curriculum, Koko accepted and was designated to study a young man named Suzuki Mambo.


==================
  Suzuki Kaito
==================
Name: Suzuki Kaito
Age: 24 years old
College Degree: Degree in Mechanical Engineering
Suzuki Kaito, graduated in mechanical engineering in England, had to come back to Japan after a plane crash killed both his parents and now has take care of his young brother that has autism. Now he lives in his old house with his brother and got a job in a famous company named, Robotics Incentive Company (RIC). Without his discernment his brother applied to a project to study people with autism and now a student of the Central University of Tokyo(CUT) will come to his house to start the project.


==================
  Suzuki Mambo
==================
Name: Suzuki Mambo
Age: 19 years old
College Degree: Dropped out High School
Suzuki Mambo, diagnosed with Aspenger Syndrome when he had 14 years old, Suzuki is extremly intelligent when it comes to drawing and perspective and because of that he ends up drawing a lot of robotics projects, part of that is the influence he had from his brother and father who are both Mechanical Engineering. 3 months before beeing diagnosed with Aspenger Syndrome Suzuki stopped going to school and even with his parents asking him to go outside he refused, causing him to drop out from High School.